  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__t">What we handle for Georgia small businesses</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:24ch;margin-bottom:12px;">The financial backbone, built and maintained.</h2>
